{
  "stem": "25651.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There's no way that I'll get permission for, for a stranger because it's-- I don't run this, this city.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You know, I'm just one of the-- anyway, my mother sends him packing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he tries and comes back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he actually has to have a word with Zlata to convince her that my mother and us two should stay in Theresienstadt and not go with her to the east.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And the two women part.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It's quite a horrendous parting, because my mother knows that you know, Zlata is going back to Poland because of-- because of her opinion and her advice.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I think my mother must have realized, for the first time, that she made a mistake.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, she made a mistake.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She didn't go to England to follow my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She must have realized earlier, as well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But the full realization probably didn't hit her until Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, my mother just wasn't up to it, because as a judge of circumstances, she was duped.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] When I was in the camps and I saw that-- you know, I was in on it when we sent the lift with all the furniture and all our stuff.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were, like, going to go get on a train and go to England.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1939.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 19-- yeah, in 1939.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, we didn't go, for reasons that my mother never explained.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I mean, you couldn't discuss that with my mother, because children were-- [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] you know, children are seen but not heard.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And things are not discussed with young children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother wouldn't even discuss things with Leo.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She wouldn't obey him.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
